>(Subject self-identifies as Lorei)
Best to mention this in the entity description.
>Sensitivity: Proportionate to circumstance

>State: Under Observation but not contained
I’d be easier to say “monitored.”
>anthro
Whether or not this is in an anthro world is unclear, but use the full term: anthropomorphic for now, until we figure it out.
>cannine

>Borzoi

>nexk

>their ability
*It’s* ability
>shulders

>co-operate

>At present, AEO-### was last intercepted in the [DATA_EXPUNGED] area of [DATA_EXPUNGED]
It’s formatted as [DATA EXPUNGED] and it’s used too much here, it’s also too vague, include at least a country.

The anomaly would also need to be heavily monitored, CEMA absolutely HAS to know the location of the entity at all times.
